## Database Schema

- All tables should follow the schema defined in docs/supabase_integration_checklist.md
- Use Row Level Security (RLS) policies for all tables
- Follow the naming conventions: snake_case for database, camelCase for Dart

## Integration Guidelines

- Always use the Supabase client from supabaseClientProvider
- Handle authentication errors gracefully
- Use transactions for multi-step operations
- Implement proper error handling and user feedback
- Follow the checklist in docs/supabase_integration_checklist.md for implementation order















